---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Testnet Portal"
  description="Boing Network testnet portal: register as developer, user, or node operator. Track metrics and qualify for rewards."
>
  <article class="portal-page">
    <nav class="portal-nav">
      <a href="/testnet" class="active">Portal</a>
      <a href="/testnet/register">Register</a>
      <a href="/testnet/developers">Developers</a>
      <a href="/testnet/users">Users</a>
      <a href="/testnet/operators">Operators</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="portal-hero">
      <h1>Testnet Portal</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Register once as a <strong>developer</strong>, <strong>user</strong>, or <strong>node operator</strong>. Get a dedicated dashboard and community page, track your metrics, and qualify for incentivized testnet rewards.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="role-cards">
      <a href="/testnet/register?role=developer" class="role-card">
        <h2>Developer</h2>
        <p>Build dApps on testnet. Register contracts for incentive tracking, qualify for grants, and share in the dedicated <strong>dApp incentive pool</strong> at mainnet (success-based, value cap per dApp).</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">Register as developer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/testnet/register?role=user" class="role-card">
        <h2>User</h2>
        <p>Use the faucet, complete quests, and share feedback. Track your quest progress and qualify for user rewards from the Community & Grants pool.</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">Register as user →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/testnet/register?role=node_operator" class="role-card">
        <h2>Node operator / Miner</h2>
        <p>Run a validator or miner, join the network with bootnodes or VibeMiner. Compete on the leaderboard and earn testnet BOING plus mainnet recognition for top operators.</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">Register as operator →</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Already registered?</h2>
      <p>Go to your role dashboard to view metrics and progress:</p>
      <div class="dashboard-links">
        <a href="/testnet/developers" class="btn btn-secondary">Developers dashboard</a>
        <a href="/testnet/users" class="btn btn-secondary">Users dashboard</a>
        <a href="/testnet/operators" class="btn btn-secondary">Operators dashboard</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Resources</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="/network/testnet">Join Testnet</a> (bootnodes, quick start) ·
        <a href="/network/faucet">Faucet</a> ·
        <a href="https://github.com/chiku524/boing.network/blob/main/docs/TESTNET-PORTAL.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TESTNET-PORTAL.md</a> ·
        <a href="https://github.com/chiku524/boing.network/blob/main/docs/INCENTIVIZED-TESTNET.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Incentivized testnet</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .portal-page { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; }
  .portal-nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }
  .portal-nav a {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .portal-nav a:hover, .portal-nav a.active { color: var(--accent-teal); }
  .portal-hero h1 { color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .lead { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .role-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .role-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(30,41,59,0.35);
    border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,0.2);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .role-card:hover { border-color: rgba(34,211,238,0.5); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(6,182,212,0.2); }
  .role-card h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .role-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.45; flex: 1; }
  .card-arrow {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent-teal);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .section { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .section h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .section p { color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .dashboard-links { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-secondary { background: rgba(34,211,238,0.15); color: var(--accent-teal); border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,0.3); }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(34,211,238,0.25); }
</style>
